{"nodes": [{"id": "plans_nimble_nebula_bricqer_image_fallback_plan", "label": "Bricqer Image Fallback Plan (nimble-nebula)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": ".kilo/plans/1780474850853-nimble-nebula.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "plans_nimble_nebula_bricqer_fallback_rationale", "label": "Bricqer-only Image Fallback Rationale", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": ".kilo/plans/1780474850853-nimble-nebula.md", "source_location": "L1", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "For part_colors with no LDraw render, attach Bricqer 'lego-visual' catalog photo into a new dedicated BRICQER_IMAGE_COLLECTION (not the rebrickable_img_url fallback). Split into two passes: 1) URL walk fills parts.bricqer_img_url, 2) per-color attach job downloads bytes only for part_colors lacking LDraw. Display priority: LDRAW > BRICQER > IMAGE."}, {"id": "plans_nimble_nebula_legovisual_integration", "label": "Bricqer LegoVisual API Integration Design", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": ".kilo/plans/1780474850853-nimble-nebula.md", "source_location": "L29", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "GET /lego-visual/item?part_type=P[&page=N]. ~95k rows, custom pagination (page= param, no page_size). Dedicated request class (not shared PaginatedRequest) to avoid leaking Rebrickable conventions. Case-insensitive bricklink_id match mirrors ImportInventoryJob::upsertProducts(). Self-dispatching job per page with 1s delay."}, {"id": "concept_bricqer_image_fallback_pipeline", "label": "Bricqer Image Fallback Pipeline", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": ".kilo/plans/1780474850853-nimble-nebula.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}], "edges": [{"source": "plans_nimble_nebula_bricqer_image_fallback_plan", "target": "plans_nimble_n